group-attribute.name: roles
group-attribute.parameter-string:
<%exec config.setAdvanced( false )%><%exec config.setDataSourceName("jdbc:minerva:sdm##")%><%exec config.setSQLQuery("SELECT urs.name
FROM [OH_SDM_Workflow].[dbo].[UserRoleSecurity] urs
INNER JOIN [OH_SDM_Workflow].[dbo].[usergroupsecurity] ugs ON urs.userGroupSecurityID = ugs.userGroupSecurityID
WHERE ugs.name = 'CHI Referrals'")%><%exec config.setOptionColumnName("name")%><%exec config.setDisplayColumnName("name")%><%exec config.setIncludeBlankOption("false")%>

group-attribute.name: CHI Centre
group-attribute.parameter-string:
<%exec config.setAdvanced( false )%><%exec config.setDataSourceName("java:comp/env/jdbc/cwsclinical")%><%exec config.setSQLQuery("select cd.id
 ,cd.code
 ,cd.normalizedCode
 ,cd.description as Description
from [CodeSet].[CodeDefinition] cd
inner join [CodeSet].[CodeSet] cs on cd.codeSetId=cs.id
where cs.identifier = 'com.orchestral.referrals.codeset.api_2_0.ReferralReceiver'")%><%exec config.setOptionColumnName("Description")%><%exec config.setDisplayColumnName("Description")%><%exec config.setIncludeBlankOption("false")%>

group.description: Users in this group can view the Appointments page containing the Sessions belonging only to the Venues that are specified in the Venue Name group attribute for this user.

group-attribute.name: VenueName
group-attribute.parameter-string:
<%exec config.setAdvanced( false )%><%exec config.setDataSourceName("java:comp/env/jdbc/BreastScreening")%><%exec config.setSQLQuery("SELECT '(' + sp.code + ') ' + v.name AS displayName, v.name FROM Venue v
INNER JOIN ServiceProvider sp on sp.serviceProviderId = v.serviceProviderId
WHERE sp.active = 'Y'
ORDER BY displayName")%><%exec config.setOptionColumnName("name")%><%exec config.setDisplayColumnName("displayName")%><%exec config.setIncludeBlankOption("false")%><%exec config.setError( "" )%>
